35:18.458 --> 35:20.166
<i>Verno says Marcus ripped it off him.</i>

35:20.250 --> 35:21.541
<i>-Got to go.</i>
-Shit…

35:21.625 --> 35:25.333
What a moron. Shit!

35:28.500 --> 35:30.625
WHAT THE HELL IS HAPPENING ON INSTA?

35:34.875 --> 35:35.750
Shit.

35:38.375 --> 35:39.416
DEAL WITH IT!!!

35:39.500 --> 35:40.375
Shit.

35:43.958 --> 35:46.250
-What a great view.
-I know. I'm sorry.

35:46.333 --> 35:48.083
Got to bounce. An emergency.

35:48.166 --> 35:50.666
-Close the door?
-We don't know each other.

35:50.750 --> 35:52.666
Don't worry. It's fine.

35:52.750 --> 35:56.791
You can steal, set the place on fire
as long as you see me again.

36:30.833 --> 36:31.791
What are you doing?

36:32.708 --> 36:35.708
A wise one once said
you should go high for perspective.

36:35.791 --> 36:36.875
You should try it.

36:39.125 --> 36:39.958
Okay.

36:40.833 --> 36:41.708
I messed up.

36:42.416 --> 36:44.500
-I admit it.
-You came to apologize?

36:45.083 --> 36:46.291
Why would I?

36:47.541 --> 36:49.916
Don't wanna be taken for an ass?
Don't talk crap.

36:50.000 --> 36:53.333
Why didn't you ask? I'd have told you.

36:55.250 --> 36:57.166
Let's hear it. Since we're here.

36:58.875 --> 36:59.708
Too late.

37:05.750 --> 37:06.708
How about a bet?

37:08.583 --> 37:09.916
Let's bet our stories.

37:10.541 --> 37:11.750
Let's play for them.

37:13.875 --> 37:16.000
Play for them? In what game?

37:18.625 --> 37:20.916
Okay. Missed. Tell me the Verno story.

37:21.916 --> 37:22.750
Okay.

37:23.666 --> 37:27.333
Verno and I used to be brothers.
We made music together.

37:27.416 --> 37:29.875
We wrote a song called "Salomé."
The hood loved it.

37:30.750 --> 37:34.000
I tried to strike a deal
with a record label.

37:34.708 --> 37:36.208
Along comes Pascal.

37:36.708 --> 37:41.125
He was willing to produce,
but he wanted a more provocative image.

37:41.833 --> 37:42.666
Provocative?

37:43.291 --> 37:46.250
I was all in. I agreed.
I wanted us to make it big.

37:47.041 --> 37:50.208
Verno didn't see it that way.
So we clashed.

37:50.791 --> 37:52.666
"Salomé" became "The Hourglass."

37:53.458 --> 37:55.125
Jean-Marc became Marcus.

37:56.291 --> 37:57.416
Verno stayed Verno.

37:58.333 --> 37:59.166
The end.

37:59.250 --> 38:02.291
-Don't get carried away. It's nothing.
<i>-You kidding?</i>

38:02.375 --> 38:05.250
Some chick kissed my man
in front of the world.

38:05.333 --> 38:07.208
-I shouldn't get carried away?
-Misunderstanding.

38:07.291 --> 38:09.833
Let's meet, have coffee,
and talk it through.

38:09.916 --> 38:13.041
<i>I'm on my way</i>
<i>to Marcus' parents' as we speak.</i>

38:14.125 --> 38:16.375
Where are you? I'll come pick you up.

38:16.458 --> 38:19.416
The whole community's behind me.
I don't need you.

38:20.541 --> 38:21.791
He's pissing me off.

38:22.458 --> 38:24.541
Tell me your biggest secret.

38:25.125 --> 38:26.416
No. It's too big.

38:26.500 --> 38:28.833
Unless you get to the top before me.

38:28.916 --> 38:31.416
-Your most awkward date?
-With a guy?

38:31.500 --> 38:34.250
That sucks, but it doesn't count. Cheater.

38:36.041 --> 38:36.916
No.

38:37.000 --> 38:38.083
Move over. No way.

38:40.708 --> 38:41.833
-Missed.
-Fuck.

38:41.916 --> 38:43.416
Something more cheerful.

38:45.500 --> 38:48.083
When was the last time you felt free?

38:48.166 --> 38:50.958
Have you seen my trials
and interview? I'm free.

38:52.583 --> 38:54.375
I didn't say free to say bullshit.

38:55.416 --> 38:56.958
Just free.

38:59.333 --> 39:00.458
That's not so easy.

39:02.458 --> 39:03.875
I have responsibilities.

39:05.916 --> 39:07.958
People expect too much from me.

39:08.041 --> 39:10.041
Fans, the media, journalists.

39:10.125 --> 39:11.625
-Family.
-Family, yeah.

39:14.208 --> 39:16.791
Everyone has a set image of who I am.

39:17.750 --> 39:18.750
It freaks me out.

39:22.333 --> 39:25.625
It's the life I've chosen.
I have to own up to it.

39:26.500 --> 39:27.875
I feel free right now.

39:28.583 --> 39:30.500
Not sure if it's because of you…

39:32.500 --> 39:34.291
-Let's hope it lasts.
-Yeah.

39:34.375 --> 39:35.666
-My turn now.
-I know.

39:35.750 --> 39:36.791
What are you doing?

39:38.708 --> 39:40.458
Not fair. It was my turn.

39:40.541 --> 39:41.958
That's freedom.

39:42.625 --> 39:44.166
That's cheating, my friend.

39:46.500 --> 39:47.333
Tell me

39:48.583 --> 39:49.416
your

39:50.208 --> 39:51.250
biggest secret.

39:52.000 --> 39:53.833
-Is that how it is?
-Yeah.

40:01.166 --> 40:03.666
My mom told you my dad left
one Christmas without warning.

40:05.416 --> 40:06.250
It's not true.

40:08.041 --> 40:08.875
Well, it is.

40:12.000 --> 40:12.916
He told me.

40:13.833 --> 40:14.708
Just me.

40:15.875 --> 40:18.500
I was little.
I wanted to protect my mom, my sister.

40:19.416 --> 40:20.416
I said nothing.

40:23.375 --> 40:24.708
A week later, he left.

40:30.666 --> 40:33.416
I still keep it to myself
because it's too late.

40:38.416 --> 40:39.750
They still don't know.

40:52.166 --> 40:53.000
Thanks.

41:05.250 --> 41:06.833
Mel! Wait!

41:06.916 --> 41:09.041
-Are you stalking me?
-Not at all.

41:09.750 --> 41:11.625
-No use showing up.
-I'm busy.

41:11.708 --> 41:14.083
Not a good idea while it's still raw.

41:14.166 --> 41:16.708
-You're going to fight.
-We love each other.

41:16.791 --> 41:18.958
-Let's talk.
-We love each other.

41:19.041 --> 41:20.208
-Let me go!
-Zack?

41:20.875 --> 41:21.875
Auntie.

41:21.958 --> 41:23.333
-Is that you?
-You okay?

41:23.416 --> 41:25.458
-What are you doing here?
-Well…

41:25.541 --> 41:28.000
-Strolling around the neighborhood.
-Hi.

41:28.083 --> 41:29.291
-And you are?
-Mel.

41:30.666 --> 41:32.291
-It's Mel.
-Which "Mel"?

41:33.333 --> 41:34.333
What do you mean?

41:34.416 --> 41:36.750
Do you often steal people's identities?

41:37.791 --> 41:39.000
I'm not the bad guy.

41:39.666 --> 41:42.583
You tried to buy us behind our backs.

41:44.750 --> 41:45.583
That's right.

41:46.833 --> 41:48.250
I have to make a call.

41:48.833 --> 41:51.333
-Should I wait for you?
-Go ahead. It's fine.

41:52.500 --> 41:53.333
Okay. I'm off.

42:01.333 --> 42:04.250
<i>Listen. Forget it.</i>
<i>"Salomé" is just a song.</i>

42:04.333 --> 42:05.708
I know. Alice told me.

42:06.625 --> 42:07.458
That's good too.

42:08.000 --> 42:12.500
-I edited the article. Added plagiarism.
-That's not what we agreed on.

42:12.583 --> 42:14.416
-It's not the point.
<i>-Now it is.</i>

42:14.500 --> 42:18.708
Do we not want to bring him down?
Everything is true. Relax.

42:18.791 --> 42:20.000
<i>Maybe it is.</i>

42:20.083 --> 42:22.625
The Simones don't do
gossip and copyrights.

42:22.708 --> 42:25.458
We don't have time for those questions.

42:25.541 --> 42:27.708
Did he mind when it came to us? No.

42:27.791 --> 42:30.041
Because he knows that everything goes.

42:30.125 --> 42:31.958
So we're publishing it now.

42:32.625 --> 42:34.541
No, I don't agree.

42:34.625 --> 42:37.041
Not this time. End of discussion.

42:39.583 --> 42:40.416
Fuck…

42:47.375 --> 42:49.750
-Are you almost done?
-I'm coming.

42:54.416 --> 42:55.250
Okay.

43:01.083 --> 43:01.916
Shit.

43:18.250 --> 43:19.750
THE SIMONES JUST POSTED A VIDEO

43:22.125 --> 43:26.041
CHRISTMAS WITH MARCUS,
PLAGIARISM AND MISOGYNY - HATS OFF!

43:26.125 --> 43:26.958
Fuck…

43:34.375 --> 43:35.875
-There you are.
-There's--

43:35.958 --> 43:37.625
I'm sorry about earlier.

43:38.416 --> 43:39.541
You nailed it.

43:40.125 --> 43:41.333
You were right there!

43:41.416 --> 43:43.750
Your flow, your lyrics. And Jean-Luc.

43:43.833 --> 43:46.000
I'm going to tell the parents.

43:46.083 --> 43:47.750
-Hold on.
-They have to hear this.

43:47.833 --> 43:48.833
Marcus, hold on!

43:49.416 --> 43:51.375
Dad? We have to talk.

43:51.458 --> 43:53.666
Indeed. You have things to explain.

43:55.333 --> 43:57.541
Who just spent Christmas in our home?

43:59.625 --> 44:02.208
Probably the one who wrote this.

44:03.625 --> 44:06.583
"Christmas with Marcus.
Plagiarism and misogyny."

44:06.666 --> 44:07.791
"Hats off!"

44:07.875 --> 44:09.458
How about that… Yeah.

44:10.583 --> 44:14.541
-Well done.
-With her vagina-scented candle.

44:14.625 --> 44:15.916
You opened the gifts?

44:18.625 --> 44:19.583
Okay. All right.

44:20.583 --> 44:23.250
-I can explain everything.
-You can try, yeah.

44:24.791 --> 44:27.208
I, for one, need a good explanation!

44:27.291 --> 44:29.833
How could you do this to your mother?
